#include <bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;
bool comp(int a,int b)
{
    return (a>b);
}
int gcd(long long int a,long long int b)
{
    if(b==0)
        return a;
    else
        return gcd(b,a%b);
}
int main(void) {
    int t,n;
    scanf("%d",&t);
    while(t--)
    {
        scanf("%d",&n);
        int a[n],i;
        bool f=0;
        for(i=0;i<n;++i)
            scanf("%d",&a[i]);
        sort(a,a+n);
        for(i=1;i<n;++i)
        {
            if(a[i]==a[i-1])
            {
                f=1;
                break;
            }
        }
        if(f)
            cout<<"NO\n";
        else
            cout<<"YES\n";
    }
    return 0;
}
